AVERY*SUNSHINE: Aw, you better
sing it like you from Philly!

00:03:04.968 --> 00:03:13.185
[LAUGHTER]

00:03:13.185 --> 00:03:14.665
AVERY*SUNSHINE: Sing sopranos!

00:03:14.665 --> 00:03:16.700
Now, altos, I know you
all-- there was only four

00:03:16.700 --> 00:03:19.183
of y'all that sang,
but I know it was more.

00:03:19.183 --> 00:03:20.766
So your part sounds
a little like this

00:03:20.766 --> 00:03:31.244
[SINGING_"DO_DO"_LOWER]
Let me hear you say it.

00:03:31.244 --> 00:03:33.144
AUDIENCE: [SINGING]

00:03:33.144 --> 00:03:35.060
AVERY*SUNSHINE: I knew
it there was more 'tos.

00:03:35.060 --> 00:03:36.491
Get it, girl.

00:03:36.491 --> 00:03:39.830
She like this, too.

00:03:39.830 --> 00:03:41.217
Get it!

00:03:41.217 --> 00:03:42.800
You all made that
last part up though.

00:03:42.800 --> 00:03:43.340
It's OK.

00:03:46.250 --> 00:03:50.660
Now tenors and basses, you sing
something that sounds like,

00:03:50.660 --> 00:03:59.458
[SINGING_"DO_DO"_LOW]

00:03:59.458 --> 00:04:00.452
Let me hear you say it.

00:04:00.452 --> 00:04:08.901
AUDIENCE: [SINGING]

00:04:08.901 --> 00:04:11.883
AVERY*SUNSHINE: Aw, don't be
trying to put no stank on it

00:04:11.883 --> 00:04:13.871
now!

00:04:13.871 --> 00:04:16.853
Now listen, if you
remember your part, great.

00:04:16.853 --> 00:04:18.344
If you don't, make something up.

00:04:18.344 --> 00:04:19.844
Now I want you to
put them together.

00:04:19.844 --> 00:04:20.734
Are you ready?

00:04:20.734 --> 00:04:22.817
If you feel the sunshine
and you see the sunshine,

00:04:22.817 --> 00:04:23.811
I need you to sing your part.

00:04:23.811 --> 00:04:24.394
Are you ready?

00:04:24.394 --> 00:04:25.171
AUDIENCE: Yeah!

00:04:25.171 --> 00:04:26.296
AVERY*SUNSHINE: Here we go.

00:04:26.296 --> 00:04:28.781
One, two, let me
hear you sing do!

00:04:28.781 --> 00:04:33.751
AUDIENCE: [SINGING]

00:04:33.751 --> 00:04:36.236
AVERY*SUNSHINE: There it is!

00:04:36.236 --> 00:04:39.218
Come on and say
it again, say it!

00:04:39.218 --> 00:04:43.194
AUDIENCE: [SINGING]

